useReducer is a hook that is used for state management 
It is an alternative to useState
UseState is built using useReducer

When to use useReducer vs useState?

useState
-Type of state is simple: (Number, String, Boolean)
-Low number of state transitions (useState calls): (a few)
-No related state transitions (related to action): No
-No business logic.
-Local State.

useReducer
-Type of state is complex: (Object or array)
-High number of state transitions: (Too many)
-Related state transitions (related to action): Yes
-Complex business logic.
-Global State.